####  Meng Wanzhou of China, the United States and Canada

### "hostage diplomacy"

The two Canadian citizens arrested in China were former diplomats, former Canadian diplomat Michael Kovrig and Canadian businessman Michaelspavor. After half a year of disappearance, China officially acknowledged that the above two were arrested for spy. This is accused of "hostage diplomacy" by Canada and the United States.

