At least since 1923, people in the cold northern region have always longed for hot summer.(Gerald Murphy)He and Sarah Murphic(SaraMurphy)Blue Coast in France(Riviera)Inventory of sunbathing. What kind of climate is the most ideal, and people have gradually formed a consensus: where there is a beach, it is sunny and the temperature is about 25 degrees Celsius.

